<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h2 style="color: #10b981;">Payment Required to Proceed</h2>

    <p>Hi <%= @recipient.name %>,</p>

    <p>The trade agreement has been fully signed! The next step is to fund the escrow account to proceed with Trade #<%= @trade.id %>.</p>

    <div style="background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Payment Details</h3>
      <p><strong>Item:</strong> <%= @trade.item&.name %></p>
      <p><strong>Amount to Pay:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@trade.price / 100.0) %></p>
      <p><strong>Seller:</strong> <%= @trade.seller.name %></p>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #ecfdf5; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid: #10b981; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #10b981;">Secure Escrow Protection</h4>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Your payment will be held securely in escrow until you receive and accept the item. This protects you as the buyer.</p>
    </div>

    <p><strong>How It Works:</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li>You fund the escrow account</li>
      <li>The seller ships the item</li>
      <li>You receive and inspect the item</li>
      <li>If accepted, funds are released to the seller</li>
      <li>If rejected, a return process begins</li>
    </ol>

    <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
      <%= link_to "Fund Escrow Now", trade_url(@trade), style: "display: inline-block; background-color: #10b981; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;" %>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
      Your payment is protected by our secure escrow system. Funds are only released when you confirm satisfaction with the item.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
